        "unitId": "circle-equation",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "choice",
        "prompt": "以 $A(1,1)$、$B(2,3)$ 为直径端点的圆的方程为（\nA.$(x-\\frac{3}{2})^2+(y-2)^2=\\frac{5}{4}$  B.$(x-\\frac{3}{2})^2+(y-2)^2=5$  C.$(x-1)^2+(y-1)^2=5$  D.$(x-2)^2+(y-3)^2=\\frac{5}{4}$）",
        "options": [
          "$(x-\\frac{3}{2})^2+(y-2)^2=\\frac{5}{4}$",
          "$(x-\\frac{3}{2})^2+(y-2)^2=5$",
          "$(x-1)^2+(y-1)^2=5$",
          "$(x-2)^2+(y-3)^2=\\frac{5}{4}$"
        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "gaokaoConnection": "圆心 $(\\frac{3}{2},2)$，$r=\\frac{\\sqrt{5}}{2}$"
      },
      {
        "id": "ag-ce4",
        "unitId": "circle-equation",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "fill",
        "prompt": "圆 $C:x^2+y^2=4$ 的圆心到直线 $x-y-2=0$ 的距离为\\underline{\\hspace{4em}}",
        "options": [],
        "answer": "$\\sqrt{2}$",
        "gaokaoConnection": "$d=\\dfrac{2}{\\sqrt{2}}=\\sqrt{2}$"
      },
      {
        "id": "ag-ce5",
        "unitId": "circle-equation",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "choice",
        "prompt": "圆 $x^2+y^2-2x-4y+4=0$ 上的点到原点的最短距离为（\nA.$\\sqrt{5}-1$  B.$\\sqrt{5}+1$  C.$\\sqrt{5}$  D.$3$）",
        "options": [
          "$\\sqrt{5}-1$",
          "$\\sqrt{5}+1$",
          "$\\sqrt{5}$",
          "$3$"
        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "gaokaoConnection": "圆心 $(1,2)$，$|OC|=\\sqrt{5}$，$r=1$，最短 $=\\sqrt{5}-1$"
      },
      {
        "id": "ag-ce6",
        "unitId": "circle-equation",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "fill",
        "prompt": "经过 $(0,0)$、$(2,0)$、$(0,2)$ 三点的圆的标准方程为\\underline{\\hspace{4em}}",
        "options": [],
        "answer": "$(x-1)^2+(y-1)^2=2$",
        "gaokaoConnection": "由对称性圆心 $(1,1)$，$r=\\sqrt{2}$"
      },
      {
        "id": "ag-ce7",
        "unitId": "circle-equation",
        "difficulty": 3,
        "type": "choice",
        "prompt": "若 $x^2+y^2+2x+ky+k^2-1=0$ 表示圆，则 $k$ 的取值范围为（\nA.$(-\\sqrt{2},\\sqrt{2})$  B.$k \\neq 0$  C.$\\mathbb{R}$  D.$(-\\infty,-2)\\cup(2,+\\infty)$）",
        "options": [
          "$(-\\sqrt{2},\\sqrt{2})$",
          "$k \\neq 0$",
          "$\\mathbb{R}$",
          "$(-\\infty,-2)\\cup(2,+\\infty)$"
        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "gaokaoConnection": "$1+1-k^2>0$，即 $k^2<2$"
      }
    ]
  },
